<A HREF="http://www.indiana-gas.com">Indiana Gas Company, Inc</A>. is Indiana

Energy's primary operating unit. Indiana Gas is a public utility that provides

local distribution of natural gas to about 470,000 residential, commercial and

industrial customers in an economically strong area covering two-thirds of the

state.  	 	</TD>

